<html>
    <head>
         <title>who am i</title>
    <head>

    <body>
         <div>
             <input>enter your name</input>
         <div>
    <body>
<html>

Absolute xpath:

/html/head/title ->to get the title
/html/body/div/input -> to get to input tag
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<html>
    <head>
         <title>who am i</title>
    <head>

    <body>
         <div>
             <label>hello</label>
         </div>
          <div>
             <input>enter your name</input>
         <div>
    <body>
<html>

Absolute xpath example 2

/html/body/div[2]/input -> to get to input tag
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Relative xpath:
//tagname[@attribute='attribute value']

hey driver go to the tag "tagname" whose attribute  "attribute" has a value of "attribute value"